# Applies to the parent build context (containing Pori/ + aloy_backend/).
# Keep the image small and avoid shipping dev cruft.

**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov

**/.venv
**/venv
**/node_modules

**/.git
**/.github
**/.gitignore

**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

**/*.md
!**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/CONTRIBUTING.md
**/ROADMAP.md
**/SECURITY.md
**/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md

**/dist
**/build
**/*.egg-info

**/tests
**/examples
**/docs

# pori runtime state
**/.pori
**/.pori_sandbox

# client and website trees are never part of the API build
aloy_backend_client
pori_website
pori_docs
